# Day 6 – Aggregate Functions

## Topics Covered

- COUNT()
- SUM()
- AVG()
- MIN()
- MAX()
- ROUND()

Count records

```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM Employee;
```

Total Salary

```sql
SELECT SUM(salary)
FROM Employee;
```

Average Salary

```sql
SELECT AVG(salary)
FROM Employee;
```

Highest Salary

```sql
SELECT MAX(salary)
FROM Employee;
```

Lowest Salary

```sql
SELECT MIN(salary)
FROM Employee;
```

Round decimal

```sql
SELECT ROUND(AVG(salary),2)
FROM Employee;
```

